mp3-archive NEWS

===========================================================================
v20260419 (2026-04-19)
===========================================================================

New features
------------
- About dialog: toolbar '?' button shows the current version read from NEWS
- Tree view — collapsed by default: directories no longer expand automatically
  on load; users can expand only the folders they need
- Tree context menu: right-clicking a file node in the tree view now shows
  the same menu as the table view ('자세히', '가사보기', '재생목록에 추가',
  '인터넷에서 정보 보기', '태그 찾기')

Bug fixes / improvements
------------------------
- Windows MSI build: fixed codepage error by replacing Korean strings with
  English equivalents in installer.wxs
- Windows MSI build: fixed ICE50 validation error by removing Icon attribute
  from the desktop shortcut (exe embedded icon is used automatically)
- Windows MSI build: added LICENSE.rtf (required by WixUIExtension license
  screen); added build/make_license_rtf.py to regenerate it from LICENSE
- Windows MSI build: improved WiX Toolset v3 auto-detection in build_msi.ps1

===========================================================================
v20260409 (2026-04-09)
===========================================================================

New features
------------
- DB per directory: SQLite database is now stored inside the selected music
  directory as `.mp3-archive.db`; switching directories automatically opens
  (or creates) the corresponding DB and runs an incremental scan
- Album art tooltip: hovering over the album column shows the embedded album
  art of that track as a tooltip image
- Tag fetch — force mode: right-clicking a row and choosing "태그 찾기" now
  opens the tag-fetch dialog even for files that already have both title and
  artist tags
- Tag fetch — auto-retry: when a search returns no results the dialog
  automatically retries using the bare filename as the keyword before giving up
- Tag fetch — no-results popup: if both the initial search and the filename
  retry return no results a notification popup is shown to the user
- Playing-row highlight (dark theme): current track is now highlighted with a
  bright blue background and bold text so it is clearly visible in dark mode
- Windows MSI installer: `build/build_msi.ps1` + `build/installer.wxs` produce
  a signed-ready MSI via WiX Toolset v3; version is read from NEWS automatically
- Linux DEB package: `build/package_deb.sh` produces a dpkg-installable
  `.deb` file; version is read from NEWS automatically

Bug fixes / improvements
------------------------
- DEB runtime crash: switched PyInstaller Linux build to onedir mode with
  `noarchive=True` and `upx=False` to prevent `pyimod02_importers` /
  `ipaddress` import errors in the installed package
- Removed album art tooltip from the filename column (was confusing)
- requirements.txt: removed unused Pillow dependency; marked pyinstaller as
  build-only comment

===========================================================================
v20260407 (2026-04-07)
===========================================================================

New features
------------
- iTunes Search: tag-fetch dialog now supports iTunes Search API as an
  alternative source; source selector lets users choose MusicBrainz,
  iTunes, or both simultaneously; iTunes results show a "출처" (source)
  column; default source switched to iTunes for better Korean music coverage
- Album art panel: dedicated panel in the player area shows the embedded
  album art of the currently playing track; displays a '♪' placeholder
  when no art is embedded
- Playlist drag-and-drop reorder: items in the playlist can now be
  dragged to a new position; the playing index stays in sync after reorder

Bug fixes
---------
- Playlist reorder: items no longer disappear when dragged (Qt internal
  MIME type is now passed through the event filter correctly)
- Code: QIcon import moved to module level; removed redundant list_files()
  call in _fill_table when search count label is updated

